inputs.name: example-aws-profile-role-63215f2a
inputs.templateBody:
AWSTemplateFormatVersion: '2010-09-09'
                Outputs:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Value: !Ref NodeGroup
                Resources:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Type: AWS::AutoScaling::AutoScalingGroup
                        Properties:
                          DesiredCapacity: 2
                          LaunchConfigurationName: example-aws-profile-role-nodeLaunchConfiguration-adf86cd
                          MinSize: 1
                          MaxSize: 2
                          VPCZoneIdentifier: ["subnet-046ff9f8793263172","subnet-0c5e98cd10212b01d","subnet-0bfdf5ed6b2167dee"]
                          Tags:
                          
                          - Key: Name
                            Value: example-aws-profile-role-eksCluster-9e45638-worker
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                          - Key: kubernetes.io/cluster/example-aws-profile-role-eksCluster-9e45638
                            Value: owned
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                        UpdatePolicy:
                          AutoScalingRollingUpdate:
                            MinInstancesInService: '1'
                            MaxBatchSize: '1'
